      <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Product Information</h4>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We make every effort to ensure that the products displayed on our
        website are accurate, up to date, and in stock. However, we do not
        guarantee the availability of products or the accuracy of descriptions
        and prices. All information is subject to change without notice.
