      <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Payment and Refund Policy</h4>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Payments for orders are processed securely through our trusted payment
        gateways. If you wish to request a refund, please refer to our Refund
